---
---
<section class='relative overflow-hidden py-16 sm:py-20 text-[#1f2a2e]'>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 via-white to-blue-50"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-32 -top-32 w-72 h-72 bg-teal-200 blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="absolute -right-24 bottom-0 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-200 blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>

  <div class='relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8'>
    <div class='max-w-4xl text-center mx-auto'>
      <p class='text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] text-teal-700 uppercase mb-3'>
         Ecomondo Mexico
      </p>
      <h2 class='text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-tight'>
        ¿Por qué <span class='text-teal-600'>participar</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class='mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600'>
        Posiciona tu marca, conecta con decisores y acelera tu crecimiento en el evento líder de sostenibilidad.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5'>
      <div class='group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl'>
        <div class='w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 grid place-items-center mb-4'>
          <img src='/icon1.webp' width='60' height='60' alt='crecimiento sostenible' loading='lazy' />
        </div>
        <p class='text-base font-semibold text-gray-800'>
          Lleve a su empresa a un crecimiento sostenible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl'>
        <div class='w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 grid place-items-center mb-4'>
          <img src='/icon2.webp' width='60' height='60' alt='negocios sostenibles' loading='lazy' />
        </div>
        <p class='text-base font-semibold text-gray-800'>
          Conviértase en pionero de los negocios verdes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl'>
        <div class='w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 grid place-items-center mb-4'>
          <img src='/icon3.webp' width='60' height='60' alt='economía circular' loading='lazy' />
        </div>
        <p class='text-base font-semibold text-gray-800'>
          Conozca las últimas tendencias e innovaciones de la industria.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl'>
        <div class='w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 grid place-items-center mb-4'>
          <img src='/icon4.webp' width='60' height='60' alt='alianza estrategica' loading='lazy' />
        </div>
        <p class='text-base font-semibold text-gray-800'>
          Genere alianzas estratégicas y expanda su red de contactos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl'>
        <div class='w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 grid place-items-center mb-4'>
          <img
            src='/icon5.webp'
            width='60'
            height='60'
            alt='conocimiento para la sostenibilidad de las industrias'
            loading='lazy'
          />
        </div>
        <p class='text-base font-semibold text-gray-800'>
          Obtenga el conocimiento más especializado para la sostenibilidad de las industrias
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>